<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Happy Birthday, My Love</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="A cinematic, scroll-driven digital love letter for a birthday celebration."
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/src/styles/main.css?v=20260705" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="chapter-rail" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="chapter-rail__line"></div>
      <div class="chapter-rail__fill"></div>
      <div class="chapter-rail__markers"></div>
    </div>

    <main class="page-shell">
      <section class="hero-section" data-reveal data-chapter-section>
        <div class="hero-copy centered-copy">
          <p class="section-label">Chapter One</p>
          <p class="eyebrow">For the woman who lights every room</p>
          <h1>From the moment I knew you, everything changed.</h1>
          <p class="hero-text">
            A love letter told one chapter at a time.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="hero-link" href="#story">Begin the story</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="story" class="story-section" data-reveal data-chapter-section>
        <div class="story-intro" data-reveal>
          <p class="section-label">Chapter Two</p>
          <p class="eyebrow">A birthday archive, made for you</p>
          <h2>Happy birthday, my love.</h2>
          <p>
            The way you light up ordinary days has made my world softer, gentler, and more beautiful. I wanted to gather the feeling of us into one little journey that unfolds as you scroll.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline">
          <div class="timeline-item" data-reveal>
            <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
            <div class="timeline-card">
              <span class="timeline-kicker">The day my world got brighter</span>
              <h3>When everything began to feel warmer.</h3>
              <p>There was a moment when your smile changed the weather inside me, and I knew life would never feel the same again.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item" data-reveal>
            <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
            <div class="timeline-card">
              <span class="timeline-kicker">Every picture we made</span>
              <h3>Little memories that learned how to glow.</h3>
              <p>Each moment with you feels like a scene I want to keep forever, soft and bright and full of wonder.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item" data-reveal>
            <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
            <div class="timeline-card">
              <span class="timeline-kicker">And every scroll since</span>
              <h3>Has felt like coming home to you.</h3>
              <p>Even the quietest days feel sweeter when they carry your warmth, your laughter, and your light.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="letters" class="letters-section" data-reveal data-chapter-section>
        <div class="section-heading" data-reveal>
          <p class="section-label">Chapter Three</p>
          <p class="eyebrow">LETTERS</p>
          <h2>Messages from the people who adore you</h2>
          
        </div>

        <div class="letters-grid empty-state-grid" id="lettersGrid">
          <!-- Grid starts empty; user-added letters will appear here. -->
          <button id="addLetter" class="letter-card letter-card--add" aria-label="Add letter" title="Add letter">
            <span class="letter-add__plus">+</span>
            <span class="letter-add__label">Add</span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="tribute-section" data-reveal data-chapter-section>
        <div class="tribute-hero" data-reveal>
          <div class="tribute-hero__content">
            <p class="section-label">Last Chapter</p>
            <p class="eyebrow">A soft closing for your special day</p>
          </div>
          <div class="scene-shell scene-shell--backdrop" data-scene-root>
            <div class="tribute-overlay">Happy Birthday,<br />Xyla</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <div class="floating-date">Date • July 8, 2026</div>
    <div class="spotify-player spotify-player--top-right" data-reveal>
      <iframe
        title="Spotify playlist"
        src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/playlist/3v1GGVObjlVMFGm4qCXFBS?utm_source=generator&theme=0"
        width="100%"
        height="152"
        frameborder="0"
        allowfullscreen=""
        allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"
        loading="lazy"
      ></iframe>
    </div>

    <script src="/dist/bundle.js?v=20260705"></script>
  </body>
</html>